    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Zinnia Labs is the speculative and applied research arm of Zinnia Holdings — designed to explore the intersections of artificial intelligence, software engineering, and digital autonomy. We challenge trends. We prototype futures. We build what others only theorize.
    </p>

    <h2>Foundations</h2>
    <p>
      Our team emerged from decades of global consulting, architecture, and government AI projects. We operate in stealth, surface with precision, and believe in research with teeth — not vaporware.
    </p>

    <h2>Domains of Interest</h2>
